{"tid":1736112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無論投唔投降 我地都冇資格批評","createTime":"2019-11-18T16:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T16:47:24.000Z","uid":175051,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50b048b665d415b2ca70972233877d668d8eea44","tid":1736112,"uid":175051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"respect<br />\n係面對咁大壓力下 無論你地決定係點都要尊重"},{"pid":"c197fd8902f86ea328bfa645b0a1288e882bb6c9","tid":1736112,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足知道你地辛苦了，但要換個角度諗，你係入面唔係受困，而係霸緊成個地方，政府付出緊消耗緊成個油尖旺區，你地係為香港人抗爭緊，政府都好焦急<br />\n<br />\n而且 佢衝到入嚟捉你嘅話 國際輿論都會俾壓力佢<br />\n有冇證據證明邊個有玩火魔法 邊個只係被困喺度<br />\n<br />\n當然如果身體受咗傷或者病咗頂唔順咁就另計<br />\n<br />\n否則 貿然咁樣自己行出嚟 投降嘅話 就救唔到自己<br />\n<br />\n就算真係行出嚟 都要係學生市民和理非嘅身份， 記住冇人知道你做過乜嘢㗎"},{"pid":"f3eda5974c0eb60db08a05dc1062488eb910a17e","tid":1736112,"uid":316753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"6d6c9524a78527f88ce58b356af479184dfa64f5","tid":1736112,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"仲有人係入邊，要講的係咁多"},{"pid":"03e70f55a1f0e16a4e48357e8da55628b2687ea9","tid":1736112,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}